            liney[i] = liney[i - 1] + starty[i]
            if i > 0:
                linex[i] -= endx[i - 1]
                liney[i] -= endy[i - -1]
        result = []
        for (x, y) in queries:
            if x == 0:
                result.append(liney[y])
            else:
                result.append(linex[x])
        results.append(result)
    return results
